// Thank you for using this cursor set.
// When adding to a CSS file do not add any of the lines that start with // like this line
// next is an example of how to add the cursor to a CSS style
// the hotspot is included in the CSS cursor 

.myDivClass {
    cursor : url('data:image/png;base64,') 23 23, pointer; 
}

// Or inline for HTML

<div style="cursor : url('data:image/png;base64,') 18 28, pointer;">
    My div has a cursor
</div>
